# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DEPENDENCIES (Ignore everywhere to force fresh installs inside container)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log
**/yarn.lock
**/package-lock.json
# Note: Keep lock files ONLY if you want deterministic builds (recommended).
# If you keep lock files, remove the two lines above.

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# BUILD ARTIFACTS (Don't copy local builds to Docker)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.next
**/.nuxt
**/.serverless

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECURITY & SECRETS (Critical!)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose.yml
**/docker-compose.*.yml
**/.dockerignore
**/npmrc
**/.npmrc

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GIT & VERSION CONTROL
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.github
**/.gitlab-ci.yml

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# EDITOR & OS FILES (Reduce noise)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# DOCUMENTATION & MISC
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/LICENSE